00:06:00.180 --> 00:06:05.240
A torus that we use--
so, this is a circle--

00:06:05.240 --> 00:06:08.100
a torus, which is
something that we sometimes

00:06:08.100 --> 00:06:12.580
think of like this,
is, on the other hand,

00:06:12.580 --> 00:06:17.030
an identification of
the following kind.

00:06:17.030 --> 00:06:18.440
Here is the x-axis.

00:06:18.440 --> 00:06:19.880
Here is the y-axis.

00:06:19.880 --> 00:06:21.590
Here is Lx.

00:06:21.590 --> 00:06:23.720
Here is Ly.

00:06:23.720 --> 00:06:34.130
And we say that any point xy is
