with x increasing by Lx.

00:06:51.500 --> 00:06:56.150
So this line is supposed
to be glued to this line.

00:06:56.150 --> 00:06:59.010
And this line is supposed
to be glued to that line.

00:06:59.010 --> 00:07:03.786
So this is identified
and this is identified.

00:07:06.910 --> 00:07:09.760
Perhaps the most intuitive
way of thinking of this

00:07:09.760 --> 00:07:14.320
