00:08:14.840 --> 00:08:16.070
There's no current.

00:08:16.070 --> 00:08:19.920
Plus dE dt,
displacement current.

00:08:19.920 --> 00:08:22.160
There's no electric field.

00:08:22.160 --> 00:08:25.040
Good equation.

00:08:25.040 --> 00:08:31.160
Curl of E is minus dB dt, no E.

00:08:31.160 --> 00:08:33.049
There's no problem, obviously.

00:08:33.049 --> 00:08:37.280
So B, for any
constant value of B,

00:08:37.280 --> 00:08:40.640
it satisfies
Maxwell's equations.

00:08:40.640 --> 00:08:44.210
So any constant
value of B should

00:08:44.210 --> 00:08:47.640
be an allowed magnetic field.

00:08:47.640 --> 00:08:52.530
Or so we would think,
