00:17:04.109 --> 00:17:06.960
x plus dy lambda.

00:17:06.960 --> 00:17:14.699
So I cancel here and I get
B0 Lx is equal to dy lambda.

00:17:17.005 --> 00:17:17.505
OK.

00:17:20.630 --> 00:17:21.210
All right.

00:17:21.210 --> 00:17:24.869
So, well, it seems that
we're succeeding again,

00:17:24.869 --> 00:17:26.220
against all odds.

00:17:26.220 --> 00:17:33.030
And we could take lambda, for
